{"tid":1304180,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"雅虎係咪無連登巴絲睇","createTime":"2019-07-10T14:05:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T14:55:05.000Z","uid":270468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"89ac5ab2ed27e6fc98644d4be20dd784b18cc3bd","tid":1304180,"uid":270468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:05:56.000Z","msg":"嚟左連登十日八日、一樣有睇雅虎入面啲新聞、但就小左睇果啲回覆、<br />\n唔睇由至可、一睇把撚火、十居其9係5毛、<br />\n想知道係咪無巴絲打睇雅虎？<br />\n一個人屌十個真係好撚攰！！<br />\n最衰我唔方便用語音輸入、<br />\n如果唔係一抽千都唔撚驚、<br />\n世伯仲用緊手寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b58ebd93556d1f9483c0c1ce983cb7813def357","tid":1304180,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:11:16.000Z","msg":"世伯點解唔學筆劃呢 簡單易用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec37e9683c2c072fb30b2fa7f751c337b6387fa5","tid":1304180,"uid":270468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b58ebd93556d1f9483c0c1ce983cb7813def357","tid":1304180,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:11:16.000Z","msg":"世伯點解唔學筆劃呢 簡單易用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:55:05.000Z","msg":"其實我以前用筆劃，溝女都係快速回覆手，但依家用緊兩部機，佢哋嘅筆劃順序唔撚同、好難適應"}]}